The campaign of All Progressives Congress, APC, governorship candidate in Imo State, Senator Hope Uzodimma, got a boost when several groups in the state endorsed him in the governorship race.
Senator Uzodimma felicitating with the groups, requested Imo people to consider votes cast for him in the forthcoming election as key to the all-round development of the southeastern state.
Senator Uzodimma was endorsed by three social groups as well as a political party for the Imo governorship election.
Leaders of the groups said Senator Uzodimma has their support for his competence and proven track records.
The governorship hopeful assured the groups of his resolve to run an all-inclusive government if elected into office at the March 9 governorship election.















